c: 11
v: 13
t: "Or they say (about the Messenger): \"He fabricates it (the Qur’an)\"? Say (to them): \"Then produce ten invented surahs like it (in eloquence, meaningfulness and truth), and call to your aid whomever you can, apart from God, if you are truthful (in your claim, not deluded or just making up excuses to justify your unbelief)"